OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A great-grandma had to have both legs  
OL,6, amputated when she became trapped under
OL,7, a double-decker bus after the driver   
OL,8, refused to let her on board.           
OL,10,FJoan Scott, then 83, was crushed under 
OL,11,Fthe vehicle's wheels in Wallsend, North
OL,12,FTyneside, on 19 September 2021.        
OL,14,FDriver Scott Cliff, 49, had refused the
OL,15,Fwidow access because he thought she had
OL,16,Fpreviously used his bus without paying.
OL,18,FHe admitted causing serious injury by  
OL,19,Fdangerous driving and was jailed for 27
OL,20,Fmonths at Newcastle Crown Court.       
